00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:07.120
So in the digital age,

00:20:07.120 --> 00:20:08.118
the one thing we do know

00:20:08.118 --> 00:20:10.790
is that the young people among us

00:20:10.790 --> 00:20:11.804
are early adopters,

00:20:11.804 --> 00:20:15.979
they are enthusiastic
adopters of new technologies.

00:20:15.979 --> 00:20:18.860
Here's some data just from 2004.

00:20:18.860 --> 00:20:21.850
We started following kids
around on their mobile devices

00:20:21.850 --> 00:20:23.180
around 2007

00:20:23.180 --> 00:20:25.504
and this just shows you
some of the changes we saw

00:20:25.504 --> 00:20:26.752
during that time.

