2018 is a last time for which we have

00:20:30.010 --> 00:20:31.620
a representative sample

00:20:31.620 --> 00:20:35.870
and 95% of adolescents now
have access to a mobile device.

00:20:35.870 --> 00:20:38.220
They're on them quite a lot.

00:20:38.220 --> 00:20:40.500
And so a recent survey showed us

00:20:40.500 --> 00:20:43.474
that tweens, those are
eight to 12 year olds,

00:20:43.474 --> 00:20:48.230
they're on 4.36 hours,

00:20:48.230 --> 00:20:50.170
and this is just for media screen time.

