households are on a screen.

00:21:09.540 --> 00:21:12.370
So there's a huge
difference in screen time

00:21:12.370 --> 00:21:15.165
based on the income level of your family.

00:21:15.165 --> 00:21:16.590
So we have a sample

00:21:16.590 --> 00:21:19.250
